            "image_border_radius": 8,
            "tab_1_enabled": true,
            "tab_1_heading": "Description",
            "tab_1_content_type": "text",
            "tab_1_text": "<p>Train harder. Recover smarter. Every session asks something of you. The Peak Performance Pack makes sure you have it. AminoLean Pre-Workout delivers clean energy from natural caffeine, with amino acids that support endurance through your hardest sets. No crash. No jitters. No artificial anything. AminoLean Creatine gives you 5g of clinically studied creatine monohydrate per serving, the most researched performance ingredient available. Strength, power output, and recovery, backed by decades of science. Together, they cover both sides of the equation. Pre-workout gets you into the session sharper. Creatine brings you out of it stronger. Two products. One system. Zero compromises.</p><p>Stay true.</p>",
            "tab_1_caption_1": "",
            "tab_1_caption_2": "",
            "tab_1_caption_3": "",
            "tab_1_caption_4": "",
            "tab_1_caption_5": "",
            "tab_1_caption_6": "",
            "tab_2_enabled": true,
            "tab_2_heading": "Nutrition",
            "tab_2_content_type": "gallery",
            "tab_2_text": "<p>Add your content here. You can use rich text formatting.</p>",
            "tab_2_image_1": "shopify://shop_images/Screenshot_2026-06-26_at_4.42.12_PM.png",
            "tab_2_caption_1": "Creatine",
            "tab_2_caption_2": "",
            "tab_2_image_3": "shopify://shop_images/Screenshot_2026-06-26_at_12.47.46_PM.png",
            "tab_2_caption_3": "AminoLean",
            "tab_2_caption_4": "",
            "tab_2_caption_5": "",
            "tab_2_caption_6": "",
            "tab_3_enabled": true,
            "tab_3_heading": "Directions",
            "tab_3_content_type": "text",
            "tab_3_text": "<p><strong>DIRECTIONS: </strong></p><p>Mix 2 scoops (1 serving) of AminoLean in 8-10 oz of cold water anytime throughout the day. For Creatine, take one scoop (1 serving) mixed with 8-10 fl. oz. of cold water (or other beverage of your choice) before, during or after training. On non-training days, take one serving (1 scoop) in the morning. Try mixing your AminoLean and Creatine together!</p><p><strong>RECOMMENDED USE of AMINOLEAN: </strong></p><p><strong>For Anytime Energy & EAA's:</strong> Take 1 or more servings first thing in the morning and/or between meals.</p><p><strong>For Pre-Workout Energy: Take 1-3 servings 20-30 minutes before training.</strong></p><p><strong>For Recovery & EAA's: Take 1-2 servings after training and/or between meals.</strong></p><p><strong>Do not exceed more than 6 scoops (3 servings) in a 4 hour period and do not exceed more than 8 scoops (4 servings) in a 24 hour period.</strong></p>",
