    "894e738c-d102-4245-8b24-f42264ccfba5": {
      "type": "amino-image-multirow",
      "blocks": {
        "template--15510886875181__894e738c-d102-4245-8b24-f42264ccfba5-167805591942128572-0": {
          "type": "row",
          "disabled": true,
          "repeater": "{{ product.metafields.product_features.image_rows.value }}",
          "settings": {
            "image": "{{ block.repeater.image.value }}",
            "heading": "{{ block.repeater.heading.value }}",
            "text": "{{ block.repeater.text | metafield_tag }}"
          }
        },
        "template--15510886875181__894e738c-d102-4245-8b24-f42264ccfba5-167805591942128572-1": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Screenshot_2026-06-26_at_11.47.06_AM.png",
            "heading": "Natural energy & power",
            "text": "<p>AminoLean provides the clean, natural spark you need to get moving, but the addition of Creatine ensures you don't redline halfway through. While Caffeine wakes up your mind, Creatine replenishes your muscles' primary energy source (ATP). Together, they provide a dual-action energy system that carries you from the first rep to the final sprint without the jitters or the crash.</p>"
          }
        },
        "row_AhH43k": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_16_2026_10_12_36_PM.png",
            "heading": "Advanced metabolic support",
            "text": "<p>True weight management is about more than just burning calories, it’s about changing your body composition. AminoLean uses L-Carnitine and CLA to help your body utilize fat for fuel. By adding Creatine, you support the development of lean muscle tissue. Since muscle is metabolically active, this bundle helps you burn more calories at rest, giving you a more toned physique and a more efficient metabolism.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--15510886875181__894e738c-d102-4245-8b24-f42264ccfba5-167805591942128572-2": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_16_2026_10_16_05_PM.png",
            "heading": "Total body recovery",
            "text": "<p>Recovery starts before you even leave the gym. AminoLean’s comprehensive EAA blend begins repairing muscle tissue in real-time, while Creatine pulls essential hydration into the muscle cells. This 'super-hydration' minimizes protein breakdown and reduces post-workout soreness. You aren't just recovering; you’re priming your body to bounce back stronger and faster for your next session.</p>"
          }
        },
        "4959ee0d-d1fe-4639-92fc-81e688e40b63": {
          "type": "row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_19_2026_11_11_51_PM.png",
            "heading": "Build and retain lean muscle",
            "text": "<p>Strong muscles mean a longer, healthier, more capable life, period. TrueFit delivers 25g of grass-fed whey per serving, the gold standard for building lean muscle and keeping it as you age.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
